(Executive Summary) Tj
T*
(- Block time: 120 seconds \(262,800 blocks/year\).) Tj
T*
(- Era size: 1,000,000 blocks \(~3.805 years\).) Tj
T*
(- Eight pre-tail eras: 50 -> 25 -> 12.5 -> 6.25 -> 3.125 -> 1.5625 -> 0.78125 -> 0.390625) Tj
T*
(ATHO/block.) Tj
T*
(- Bootstrap allocation: 390,625 ATHO at block 1 \(included in total pre-tail base\).) Tj
T*
(- Tail starts at height 8,000,000 \(~30.44 years\) at 0.1953125 ATHO/block.) Tj
T*
(- Tail annual issuance: 51,328.125 ATHO/year.) Tj
T*
(- Hard max supply cap: 150,000,000 ATHO.) Tj
T*
(- Fee floor: 350 atoms/vB \(3.5e-7 ATHO/vB\).) Tj
T*
(- Fee routing: pre-tail 40% to consensus pool, post-tail 55% to consensus pool.) Tj
T*
(- Tail burn target on non-pool share: 100% burn / 0% miner, with floor clipping.) Tj
T*
(- Supply floor: 21,000,000 ATHO.) Tj
T*
(- Protocol deflation threshold: ~35.43% sustained utilization.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Emission Schedule) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
