T*
() Tj
T*
(Total pre-tail base including bootstrap:) Tj
T*
(- 99,609,375 ATHO subsidy path + 390,625 ATHO bootstrap at block 1 = 100,000,000 ATHO.) Tj
T*
(- Remaining mintable headroom after pre-tail base: 50,000,000 ATHO \(tail subsidy only, then) Tj
T*
(subsidy suppresses to zero\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Hard-cap rule:) Tj
T*
(- total_supply <= 150,000,000 ATHO.) Tj
T*
(- Subsidy is clipped at coinbase by remaining cap headroom.) Tj
T*
(- After cap is reached, subsidy remains 0 and fees continue through the same burn/pool paths.) Tj
T*
