T*
(Fee and Burn Math) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Per block at full utilization) Tj
T*
(- Total fee capacity at floor: 3,500,000 * 350 = 1,225,000,000 atoms = 1.225 ATHO) Tj
T*
(- Routed-to-pool share at tail \(55%\): 0.67375 ATHO) Tj
T*
(- Burn-path share at tail \(45%\): 0.55125 ATHO) Tj
T*
(- Tail issuance per block: 0.1953125 ATHO) Tj
T*
(- Net per-block formula: Delta_block = 0.1953125 - \(0.55125 * utilization\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Per year at full utilization) Tj
T*
(- Tail issuance: 0.1953125 * 262,800 = 51,328.125 ATHO/year) Tj
T*
(- Total annual fees at floor: 321,930 ATHO/year) Tj
T*
(- Annual burn-path max \(45%\): 144,868.5 ATHO/year) Tj
T*
(- Annual net formula: Delta_year = 51,328.125 - \(144,868.5 * utilization\)) Tj
T*
(- Formula above applies while subsidy is still positive; after hard-cap clip, subsidy term is 0.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Deflation Threshold) Tj
T*
(Set annual net to zero:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(51,328.125 - 144,868.5u = 0) Tj
T*
(u = 51,328.125 / 144,868.5 ~= 0.3543) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(So:) Tj
T*
(- <35.43%: inflationary protocol net.) Tj
T*
(- =35.43%: neutral.) Tj
T*
(- >35.43%: deflationary protocol net \(until floor clipping binds\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Post-tail net annual change by utilization) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(| Utilization | Net annual change |) Tj
T*
(|---:|---:|) Tj
T*
(| 0% | +51,328.125 ATHO/year |) Tj
T*
(| 25% | +15,110.999 ATHO/year |) Tj
T*
(| 30% | +7,867.575 ATHO/year |) Tj
T*
(| 35.43% | ~0 ATHO/year |) Tj
T*
(| 40% | -6,619.275 ATHO/year |) Tj
T*
(| 50% | -21,106.125 ATHO/year |) Tj
T*
(| 75% | -57,323.250 ATHO/year |) Tj
T*
(| 100% | -93,540.375 ATHO/year |) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Floor-Clipped Burn Behavior) Tj
T*
(Burn is constrained by available headroom:) Tj
T*
(- burn_headroom = emitted_up_to - cumulative_burned_before - supply_floor) Tj
T*
(- effective_burn = min\(desired_burn, routed_non_pool_fees, burn_headroom\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Implications:) Tj
T*
(- Consensus cannot burn below 21,000,000 ATHO effective circulating supply.) Tj
T*
(- At/near floor, burn is clipped to available headroom.) Tj
T*
(- Unburned routed fees fall through to miner accounting for exact coinbase closure.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Coinbase and Accounting Invariants) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
