(Atho?s active model is:) Tj
T*
(- **100M total pre-tail base over ~30.44 years** \(99.609375M subsidy + 390,625 bootstrap\),) Tj
T*
(- then fixed tail subsidy \(0.1953125 ATHO/block\) until clipped by hard-cap headroom,) Tj
T*
(- with pool-routed fees and burn on routed non-pool share,) Tj
T*
(- with a hard max emitted supply cap of **150,000,000 ATHO**,) Tj
T*
(- and a hard **21M supply floor**.) Tj
T*
() Tj
